#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.38"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.38:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.38:0.2"
msgid "4. Paṭipattivagga "
msgstr "4. Practice "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.38:0.3"
msgid "38. Dutiyabrahmaññasutta "
msgstr "38. The Brahmin Life (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.38:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.38:1.2"
msgid "“Brahmaññañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, brahmaññatthañca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you life as a brahmin and the goal of life as a brahmin. "

msgctxt "sn45.38:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.38:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, brahmaññaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is life as a brahmin? "

msgctxt "sn45.38:1.5"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn45.38:1.6"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.38:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmaññaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called life as a brahmin. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.38:1.8"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, brahmaññattho? "
msgstr "And what is the goal of life as a brahmin? "

msgctxt "sn45.38:1.9"
msgid "Yo kho, bhikkhave, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn45.38:1.10"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmaññattho”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the goal of life as a brahmin.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.38:1.11"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
